name: At Home Canada 2012 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .H12 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Since the H12 file extension is used by the 2012 version of At Home Canada, most H12 files are created in 2013 (the following year).
NOTE: H&R Block Canada At Home became H&R Block Canada Tax Software in 2013.

description: Tax return saved by H&R Block Canada 2012, a Canadian tax preparation program; contains Canadian federal income tax forms and user-entered tax data; saves the progress of a tax return so it can be resumed at a later time.
